for assessing the extent of\nmisspecification bias arising due to TWFE regressions. Finally, we propose\nalternative (and simple) estimation strategies that can circumvent these issues\nwith two-way fixed regressions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Feb 2022 01:50:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 May 2023 21:38:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-22"}
