adeoff, which we show is an NP-hard\nsignomial programming problem. We finally solve this problem through proposing\na general optimization solver. Our numerical results reveal new findings on the\ninterdependencies between the idle times in-between the global aggregations,\nmodel/concept drift, and D2D cooperation configuration.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Feb 2022 05:11:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 Feb 2022 20:00:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 12 Feb 2022 03:54:59 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 17 Feb 2022 19:41:25 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Sat, 22 Oct 2022 19:02:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-25"}
