ong lensing modelling where the quest for the best\nfit model will be balanced by the quest for presenting a physically motivated\nmass model, in particular by imposing priors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Feb 2022 08:20:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Jun 2022 09:11:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-17"}
