e driver code shipped with the\nSDK of STMicroelectronics and three zero-day bugs in the SDK of NXP. Eight CVEs\nhave been allocated for them. Considering the wide adoption of vendor SDKs in\nreal products, our results are alarming.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Feb 2022 09:10:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 Feb 2022 00:40:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 19 Apr 2022 04:50:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-20"}
