c\nordering is the most favourable one except for the near vicinity of the fcc\nstructure and the magnetic exchange is expected to be of RKKY type.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Feb 2022 14:15:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 12 May 2022 08:42:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-02"}
