e as mobile probes. The results show the proposed\ntravel-delay-based model generates lower delay with non-full penetration rate\nthan the benchmark models with full penetration rate under certain traffic\nconditions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Feb 2022 15:24:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 22 Jun 2022 14:52:19 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 13 Oct 2022 03:51:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-14"}
