 goal in a\nsubsequent paper. Based critically on said low functional level where\ncompatibility conditions are not recognized, the subsequent paper solves in the\naffirmative a presently open problem: whether uniform stabilization by\nlocalized tangential boundary feedback controls, which-in addition-are finite\ndimensional, is also possible in dim $\\Omega = 3$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Feb 2022 15:37:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-10"}
